Package Shared

Class Grade

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shared.Grade
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Grade
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Provides data fields and methods to create a Java data-type, representing a Grade in a Learning Platform Java application. The overall purpose of this class is to store information to display and send between the client and server, and to be used to Grade assignments by the professor user.
